很抱歉，由于我是以纯文本形式进行回答，我无法直接提供LaTeX代码。不过，你可以尝试以下代码片段来编译你的示例：

```latex
\documentclass{article}
\usepackage{amsmath}
\usepackage{booktabs}

\begin{document}

In the experiment, Alice, Bob and Charlie use the same parameters because of symmetric channel loss. We denote $\mu_{2}$, $\mu_{1}$, $\mu_{0}$ to be the intensity of signal state, decoy state, vacuum state respectively, $P^{Z(X)}_{\mu}$ to be the probability of Z(X) basis for corresponding intensity $\mu$. Experimental parameters are shown in Table \ref{tab:parameters}.

\begin{table}[ht]
\centering
\begin{tabular}{ccc}
\toprule
Parameter & Description & Value \\
\midrule
$\mu_{2}$ & Intensity of signal state & \textit{value} \\
$\mu_{1}$ & Intensity of decoy state & \textit{value} \\
$\mu_{0}$ & Intensity of vacuum state & \textit{value} \\
$P^{Z(X)}_{\mu}$ & Probability of Z(X) basis & \textit{value} \\
\bottomrule
\end{tabular}
\caption{Experimental Parameters}
\label{tab:parameters}
\end{table}

\end{document}
```

请确保你的LaTeX环境已正确设置并包含所需的宏包（如amsmath和booktabs）。此外，将`\textit{value}`替换为适当的数值。希望这可以帮助你编译正确的文档。
